page.title: 12SHOWING DOGS BY LOUISE
page.content: We have 2 dogs;a{Whippet}called Penny and a{Cairn}terrier called Sophie. Penny is 13 and Sophie is 2.Sophie had 5 puppies;1 died.We are selling the boys for Â£95 each and the bitch for Â£105.We are breeding Cairns and we will buy a{Rottweiler}and breed from her.We take them to match meetings once a fortnight and for walks at 6.30,7.30 and 8.15am and at4pm,6pm & 8pm.When I leave school I am going to learn how to wash,clip and pluck dogs and eventually my family want to own some kennels. LOUISE WARDMAN {DISCO DANCING BY VICTORIA DANNATT My hobby is disco dancing.I go to weekly classes.I am working for my Gold Medal.I like dancing to Duran Duran.Some of my steps are Step Bol Change,Train,Hula and Swimming Steps.It is difficult to do and it keeps me fit.
